Name: Hentai Breakout City
About the game: Welcome to Hentai Breakout City, an Indie game based on the classic Breakout. OBJECTIVES Your objective is to break all the blocks. For each number of blocks eliminated you remove a piece of clothing from the character's level. Beat each level to unlock items in the gallery and other levels. FEATURES • Power Ups • Different girl in each level. • Browse the gallery with one hand.
